Run on Vagrant
1. Start Vagrant
  - vagrant up
  - vagrant ssh
Install Node.js (if not installed)
  - sudo apt update
  - sudo apt install nodejs npm
Navigate to your project directory
  - cd /vagrant/registration-app
start the server
  - node server.js
Visit http://localhost:3000 for AJAX, but open index.html via your browser or Live Server in VS Code (host port forwarding may be required).





